message.text:
Calling all future People Managers!

The JPMAP-FEU Chapter has officially opened its applications! ✨

Here’s everything you need to start your journey with us:

📌 Application Form: 
https://forms.office.com/r/2vJGHzsGP2
https://forms.office.com/r/2vJGHzsGP2
https://forms.office.com/r/2vJGHzsGP2

📖 Application Guidelines: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1Dy4GMV1UBmKS6LPqIuQIz9-rGJK5ERTpBGXixASRfso/edit?usp=sharing 

🏛 Specific Department Descriptions: https://docs.google.com/document/d/19wa8IfGPBqKdWDa9WJBQcgq3EkCaPefL-kays2cK3l8/edit?usp=drivesdk

Don’t miss this chance to belong, lead, and grow with fellow people managers. Together, let’s make an impact!

#JPMAPFEUChapter 
#JPMAPFEU_13 
#JPMAPapaibigKaSaIloilo

message.text:
Calling all future People Managers!

The JPMAP-FEU Chapter has officially opened its applications! ✨

Here’s everything you need to start your journey with us:

📌 Application Form: 
https://forms.office.com/r/2vJGHzsGP2
https://forms.office.com/r/2vJGHzsGP2
https://forms.office.com/r/2vJGHzsGP2

📖 Application Guidelines: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1Dy4GMV1UBmKS6LPqIuQIz9-rGJK5ERTpBGXixASRfso/edit?usp=sharing 

🏛 Specific Department Descriptions: https://docs.google.com/document/d/19wa8IfGPBqKdWDa9WJBQcgq3EkCaPefL-kays2cK3l8/edit?usp=drivesdk

Don’t miss this chance to belong, lead, and grow with fellow people managers. Together, let’s make an impact!

#JPMAPFEUChapter 
#JPMAPFEU_13 
#JPMAPapaibigKaSaIloilo
